Dearest, I feel quite safe dealing with you in this important
business. Through this medium (Internet) has been greatly abused, I
choose to reach you through it because it still remains the fastest
medium of communication. Please consider this mail with all
seriousness as I seek for your partnership from my spirit in this
business transaction, should you be interested kindly reply me for
more details
Most  importantly , I’ m choosing you as a foreign partner and at the
same time assuring  you that this transaction is 100% risk and trouble
free to both  parties. I contacted you believing that you will not let
me down once you get this mail and after this transaction takes place
under your care, then more details of this proposal will be forwarded
to you as soon as I hear from you positively concerning this transfer.

Best Regards.

Mr Saeed Yahyah.
